2,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"再讀咪曬時間<br />\n個個讀書都掂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"以前返part time廚整到腰，之後讀返書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba6088860727b04e8ed6156b17ceadaa953cb43","tid":2118742,"uid":28007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c451e94773d3d65bd41aa8a855ed6b9e322962cb","tid":2118742,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"其實出到去大場無人理你有無讀過張沙紙<br />\n廚藝hd係會教你啲廚房基本知識<br />\n不過間間場唔同 個個師傅手法唔同<br />\n你點都要從頭學過<br />\n<br />\n以前我會叫人唔好曬錢<br />\n<br />\n依家我會叫你讀下 睇定啲先 亨受多一排青春<br />\n攞張沙紙（尤其是中廚）移民好似加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0749d703216995397a19009a988bed7840c1f7a4","tid":2118742,"uid":342036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"不如你講下個歷程係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當俾其他考生一個參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8feebace8c822e0dc99cafbeb7eb69cd7d5824","tid":2118742,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"做茶記不如做點心"},{"pid":"f9625b6bb6be3d5280fd282978c927010386b5b1","tid":2118742,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"好事嚟，升唔到專業科目degree 學門手藝仲易移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7835b457828b6aa708db1ce84da1c0eb916bfc35","tid":2118742,"uid":28007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0749d703216995397a19009a988bed7840c1f7a4","tid":2118742,"uid":342036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"不如你講下個歷程係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當俾其他考生一個參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"其實我就太多原因dse都無讀就出左黎拋<br />\n首先學門手藝就一定要講興趣<br />\n<br />\n唔理剪頭髮又好 煮野都好<br />\n無興趣既話就點都唔會學得好<br />\n一定要用時間去從新適應<br />\n<br />\n同以往讀書唔同<br />\n唔可以講死背 死溫爛溫 <br />\n要用時間去浸淫<br />\n師傅（老師）大多數都係老屎忽/未必對你好<br />\n亦都唔會有讀書時期既同學陪你一齊<br />\n<br />\n同埋已經踏足左社會 <br />\n要為自己負責 轉變好大<br />\n但係適應左就會無事<br />\n<br />\n之不過當決定左要學門手藝 <br />\n就唔好拖<br />\n手藝愈早學一定愈好 <br />\n年紀愈大 反而學習依方面既能力會愈低 <br />\n同埋20幾歲左右就可以開始穩定 <br />\n用門手藝去開鋪頭都易好多 因為仲有大多年輕本錢去輸<br />\n<br />\n其實我一直都好羨慕我啲朋友讀大學hehehaha<br />\n但係我都有唔少朋友同我講 <br />\n佢地好恨我有目標 有技能 一定無死<br />\n<br />\n頭幾年一定會係辛苦 <br />\n如果真係攰 咪好似學下我咁上連登開個post打下飛機<br />\n<br />\n如果你同我講你讀書唔掂 <br />\n我為你好就會叫你hea埋幾年 老閪都讀上去<br />\n我為你將來好就會叫你啦啦林去學門手藝 唔好比自己後悔一世仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da1b3472dd78514dc18553454f1c50bd6134406","tid":2118742,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:11:42.000Z","msg":"好多飲食都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718c6a59aae26bec3709f4c5b9b30b30ab0f6b5e","tid":2118742,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9625b6bb6be3d5280fd282978c927010386b5b1","tid":2118742,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"好事嚟，升唔到專業科目degree 學門手藝仲易移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:12:02.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 但係我都有聽過下朋友同我講我會易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要我鋪頭出番張紙證明我係做中廚就得<br />\n姐係我自己出比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"